Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeehaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Over in a flash again, my dude!}Không hổ danh đại ca!
