Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{In through the nose, out through the mouth.}Hít vào bằng mũi và thở ra bằng miệng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Boss.}Cảm ơn chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{I see it!}Mình có thể thấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Dammit! We're getting nowhere!}Chết tiệt! Chẳng tới đâu cả!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{We're taking down as many as we can!}Cứ hạ càng nhiều càng tốt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{Look over there.}Nhìn bên kia kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's a Tanker, right?}Tanker nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Damn!}Chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank goodness you're okay!}May quá, mày vẫn ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Are you happy, too, Pipe?}Mày vui lắm hả, Pipe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{What was that?}Gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What was that?}Đ-Đó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Stay in here.}Vào trong đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{--Shit!\N--It's too much.}Chết tiệt!\N Không ổn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{Watch out!}Cẩn thận!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's heading for Deca-dence! After it!}Nó đang hướng đến Deca-Dence! Bám theo!
