Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{"Mundy"\NDid we get 'em all?}Dọn dẹp xong chưa nhỉ?\N Mundy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's that?}Gì thế kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Commander, look!}Đội trưởng, nhìn xem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{All units back off! Get back!}Tất cả rút lui! Chạy mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is that thing?}Thứ quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now! Fire!}Bắn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{--It's no use!\N--It's too tough.}Không ổn! Nó cứng quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{Get in close!}Tiếp cận gần hơn xem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Why you...}Sao mày dám...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now!}Ngay lúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{These are some twig legs you got!}Đây là chân mày nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Lemme see your ugly mug!}Cho tao xem cơ thể xấu xí của mày nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Say goodnight!}Ngủ ngon nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{That's Kurenai for you!}Không hổ là Kurenai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Incredible!}Thật khó tin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{The strongest Tanker...}Tanker mạnh nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{That was some nice work back there.}Lúc này em làm tốt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{What? Um... I...}Hả? À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{I did what I could to help!}Không có gì ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Um... It was an honor to f-f-fight\Nalongside you, Kurenai, ma'am.}T-Thật vinh dự khi được chiến đấu cùng chị, Kurenai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{My name is Natsume!}Tên em là Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{I don't recognize you.}Gương mặt mới à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{What's your unit?}Đơn vị của em đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, uh... actually I'm not in The Power...}Thực ra... em không thuộc The Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{How come?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm a bug...}Em chỉ là một con bọ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{A "bug"?}Bọ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{I'm told it means I'm weak like an insect.}Tức là yếu như mấy con côn trùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{--Hey, stay still.\N--That's wild.}Này, yên nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Who said that about you?}Ai nói vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{If you're an insect, Sou and Ryoku are boogers.}Nếu em là bọ thì Sou và Ryoku \Nchắc là một đống chất nhầy quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{fight with us as part of The Power.}hãy cùng chiến đấu với bọn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{I... b-but...}Em... nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{We won't turn away someone\Nwho possess the will to fight.}Bọn chị sẽ luôn chào đón những người có ý chí chiến đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{Welcome to The Power.}Chào mừng đến với The Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{--Hooray!\N--Glad to have ya!}Tuyệt vời! \N Hay lắm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{We got your back!}Cố gắng lên nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{--You're in.\N--Thanks!}Chào mừng em!\N Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Boss!}Ông chủ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{I did it!}Cháu làm được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{It's all thanks to you! Thank you so much!}Nhờ chú cả đó! Cảm ơn chú rất nhiều!
