Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{Sir, wh-wh-what brings you here?}N-Ngài làm gì ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{--"Kabu"? "Sir"?\N--H-Have you returned to active duty?}Kabu? Ngài? 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{--She hasn't changed.\N--I can hardly believe it.}Vẫn chẳng thay đổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, to get to meet on the battlefield again!}Chúng ta lại gặp nhau trên chiến trường rồi.
